Deploy `ArtCenterDAO` to any EVM-compatible network that supports Solidity
0.8.20.

Members can submit proposal descriptions, vote for or against each proposal,
and execute proposals that receive more support than opposition. Each address
can vote only once per proposal.

Contributors can send ETH through `contribute()` and later withdraw from their
own tracked balance with `withdrawFunds(uint256 amount)`.

The contract emits events for proposal submissions, votes, proposal execution,
contributions, and withdrawals so a frontend or indexer can follow DAO activity.
